\b I have updated some of my man pages and I keep getting the old page?
\b0 \
\
Bwana caches the HTML formatted man page so that it doesn't have to recreate commonly accessed pages more than once. Delete the caches folder to create new copies, the folder is located in your home folder ~/Library/Caches/Bwana.\
